🔒 Privacy Policy — Charades

Last Updated: January 2026

Charades respects your privacy and is committed to protecting it. This Privacy Policy explains how your information is handled when you use the Charades application.

1. Information We Collect:
Charades does not collect, store, transmit, or share any personal information.
The app runs entirely offline and all gameplay happens locally on your device.

2. Non-Personal Data:
Charades does not collect:
-Names, email addresses, or contact details
-Device identifiers or hardware information
-Location data
-Usage analytics or tracking data
-Cookies or similar technologies

3. Internet & Permissions
Charades:
-Does not require an internet connection
-Does not access system files, camera, microphone, or contacts
-Does not request special permissions

4. Third-Party Services:
Charades does not integrate with any third-party services, SDKs, analytics tools, or advertising networks.

5. Children’s Privacy:
Charades is safe for all ages. Since no personal data is collected, the app complies with children’s privacy protection standards.

6. Data Security:
Because no data is collected or stored, there is no risk of data leakage or misuse.

7. Changes to This Policy:
If this Privacy Policy is updated, the revised version will be made available within the app or its store listing.

8. Contact:
If you have questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact the developer through the platform where you downloaded Charades.
